description: Lists the associations for the specified VPC endpoint.

parameters.name: resourceConfigurationIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID for the resource configuration associated with the VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: Information about the VPC endpoint associations.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the VPC endpoint association.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the VPC endpoint association was created, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: createdBy
nested_items.description: The account that created the association.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the VPC endpoint association.

nested_items.name: resourceConfigurationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource configuration.

nested_items.name: resourceConfigurationId
nested_items.description: The ID of the resource configuration.

nested_items.name: resourceConfigurationName
nested_items.description: The name of the resource configuration.

nested_items.name: vpcEndpointId
nested_items.description: The ID of the VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: vpcEndpointOwner
nested_items.description: The owner of the VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, a pagination token for the next page of results.
